  "title": "(ADT) Production Supervisors needed /  $3200 to $4200",
  "description": "<p>👀CONTRACT PRODUCTION SUPERVISORS NEEDED👀</p><p></p><p>📍 Location: West (Transport provided at Jurong East, Tampines and Sengkang MRT)</p><p>🕧 Working hours: Mon to Fri- 830am to 530pm</p><p>💰 Salary: $3200 to $4200</p><p></p><p>✨AN ADVANTAGE IF HAVE WAREHOUSE/PRODUCTION EXPERIENCE✨</p><p></p><p>📝Job Scope:</p><p>👀 Responsibility for determining the best and most efficient uses of the available resources, including equipment and labor, to meet production goal.</p><p></p><p>👀 Assign job duties, determine equipment and supplies required, and build a production schedule.</p><p></p><p>👀 Hires and trains the workforce for a project.</p><p></p><p>👀 Manage and motivate the staff, monitoring them to ensure they meet performance and safety requirements.</p><p></p><p>👀 Dealing with and resolving problems and issues which arise.</p><p></p><p>👀Monitoring & reporting on standards & performance targets.</p><p></p><p>Applicants who are interested, pls email to recruit@onehirestaffing.com or call 6031 4933</p><p>1. Full Name</p><p>2. Residential Location</p><p>3. Start/End Date</p><p></p><p>R1104563 (Tan Si Ni Shirley Gwen)</p><p>EA License: 25C3058 (One Hire Staffing Pte Ltd)</p>",
